<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Register</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Abril+Fatface&family=Agbalumo&family=Anton&family=Exo+2:wght@900&family=Kalnia:wght@500&family=Lobster&family=Major+Mono+Display&family=Pacifico&family=Bungee&family=Poppins:wght@300;700&family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,300;0,500;0,900;1,900&family=Tilt+Neon&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-dark">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-dark">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <a
          class="navbar-brand"
          href="/"
          style="
            font-family: 'Bungee', sans-serif;
            font-size: xxx-large;
            color: white;
          "
          >//Redemy.</a
        >
        <button
          class="navbar-toggler"
          type="button"
          data-bs-toggle="collapse"
          data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent"
          aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-label="Toggle navigation"
        >
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <h2
      style="
        text-align: center;
        font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
        font-size: xx-large;
        margin-top: 30px;
        color: white;
      "
    >
      SIGN UP
    </h2>
    <div class="container">
      <form action="/register" method="post">
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label
            for="exampleFormControlInput1"
            class="form-label"
            style="
              font-size: larger;
              font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
              color: white;
            "
            >User Name</label
          >
          <input
            type="text"
            class="form-control"
            placeholder="name"
            name="username"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label
            for="exampleFormControlInput1"
            class="form-label"
            style="
              font-size: larger;
              font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
              color: white;
            "
            >Email address</label
          >
          <input
            type="email"
            class="form-control"
            placeholder="name@example.com"
            name="email"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label
            for="exampleFormControlInput1"
            class="form-label"
            style="
              font-size: larger;
              font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
              color: white;
            "
            >Password</label
          >
          <input type="text" class="form-control" name="password" placeholder="*****"/>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label
            for="exampleFormControlInput1"
            class="form-label"
            style="
              font-size: larger;
              font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
              color: white;
            "
            >Role</label
          >
          <select
            class="form-select"
            aria-label="Default select example"
            name="role"
          >
            <option selected disabled>Choose Role..</option>
            <option value="user">User</option>
            <option value="admin">Admin</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="d-grid gap-2 col-2 mx-auto mt-5 mb-5">
          <button
            class="btn btn-secondary"
            type="submit"
            value="register"
            style="font-size: x-large; font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif"
          >
            Confirm
          </button>
        </div>
        <div
          class="card text-bg-secondary mb-3 mx-auto"
          style="max-width: 18rem"
        >
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5
              class="card-title"
              style="
                text-align: center;
                font-size: x-large;
                font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
              "
            >
              Attention Hints!
            </h5>
            <p class="card-text">
              Registrasi terlebih dahulu dengan memasukkan Nama, Email, Password
              anda. Untuk Role anda adalah pengguna/bukan Admin maka pilih User
              dan sebaliknya jika anda adalah Admin maka pilih Role Admin.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>
      <footer class="bg-dark text-light text-center py-4" style="margin-top: 10%;">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <h4 class="mb-3" style="font-family:'Bungee',sans-serif;">//Redemy.</h4>
              <p>
                Easiest way to upgrade your Skills
                Your platform for IT courses and learning resources.
                <br/>"Empowering Minds, Elevating Futures: Bridging Education and Technology"
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <h4 class="mb-3"style="font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif; font-weight: bolder;">Contact Us</h4>
              <p>Email: info@redemy.com</p>
              <p>Phone: (123) 456-7890</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <h4 class="mb-3" style="font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif; font-weight: bolder;">Online Course</h4>
              <p>Available list course:</p>
              <p>1. Build Web Using HTML5, CSS3, & Bootstrap</p>
              <p>2. Node.js, Express & MongoDB Dev to Deployment</p>
              <p>3. Build Web Apps with Vue.JS2 & Firebase</p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-10" style="text-align: center;margin-top: 1%;">
              <h4 class="mb-3" style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;">Â© 2023 Copyright:</h4><p>Website for //Redemy. "Online Course"</p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
